for the Beijing Women&#146;s conference, Guadelajara, Mexico.  PANEL # 1:
Desarrollo del Capital Human y Reduccion de la Pobreza;  FORO REGIONAL, "La
Mujer in las Americas: Participacion y Desarrollo"Guadalajara, 5-7 abril de
1994	<p>

<a href=evans-my.html>IMPROVING PROGRAM ACTIONS TO
       MEET THE INTERSECTING NEEDS OF WOMEN AND CHILDREN
