article prepared for the section on &#147;Marriage and the Family&#148; of the
Encyclopedia of Third World Women, May 1995.  Nellie P. Stromquist (Chief
Editor) <br><p> 

<a href=crwrepo.html>Childrearing Practices and Beliefs in Sub-Saharan Africa </a>by Judith L.
Evans Report of a workshop held in Windhoek, Namibia October, 26-29, 1993.
Sponsored by UNICEF and organized by the Consultative Group on ECCD.<br><p>


