<title>Reports from meetings in 1995, posted by members of the CG and friends of
ECCD
</title>
<h1>Reports from meetings in 1995, posted by members of the CG and friends of
ECCD</h1>
 <IMG SRC="blue.gif" ALT="*"> <A HREF="pdcbe.html">Participatory Development Communication and Basic Education. Needs and
Perspectives within the Context of West and Central Africa</A><p>
