infants orient to sounds.  <u>Child Development</u>, <u>50</u>, 431-36.<p>
<sup>2</sup> 	Haith, M. N., Berman, T., and Moore, M.J. (1977).  Eye contact
and face scanning in early infancy.  <u>Science</u>, <u>198</u>, 853-855.<p>
