<title>Child Care Programmes As An Entry Point 
For 
Maternal And Child Health Components Of 
Primary Health Care
</title><body><p>
<p>
<center>
<b>CHILD CARE PROGRAMMES AS AN ENTRY POINT </b><br>
<b>FOR </b><br>
<b>MATERNAL AND CHILD HEALTH COMPONENTS OF </b><br>
<b>PRIMARY HEALTH CARE</b><p>
</center>
<p>
Maternal and Child Health and Family Planning <br>
Division of Family Health<br>
World Health Organization<br>
Geneva<br>
<p>
